email_content:
Hi Sarah,

I hope you’re doing well! I wanted to give you a brief update on the newest admissions cycle here at Prestige University:

• Applications rose by 5%, reaching roughly 15,000.
• The acceptance rate dipped to 7%, so we welcomed 1,050 exceptional admits.
• Average scores climbed to a 1480 SAT and a 33 ACT.
• The incoming class represents students from more than 60 countries, making this our most diverse cohort yet.

We’re thrilled about the energy this group will bring when they arrive on campus in late August. I’ll keep you posted as orientation details and potential alumni-student engagement opportunities take shape, but feel free to reach out if you’d like any additional information in the meantime.

Thanks for all you do for the Prestige community!

Best,
[Your Name]
Admissions Office
Prestige University
